race.description: Girls Day Out On Sale Now C,G&E Bm70 Handicap
race.comment: EARL OF BANTRY (1) was game in defeat first-up at Toowoomba then featured in the market but didn't handle the class rise in the $500k Country Cup at the Gold Coast last start. Has an outstanding record at this distance and the third-up form is strong so he looks a big chance under today's scenario. LAND BANK (19) had been racing well without winning then really stamped himself last start with a dominant victory over today's journey at Ipswich. Tackles a far better race this time but he drops 4kgs and should be competitive. RAMP IT UP (7) is racing well and is ready to peak third-up. Wide draw a bit of a niggle, but hopefully he won't get too far back. TOO MANY THOUGHTS (9) is flying this prep and gets in well after the claim. Can easily make it four wins from his last five starts.
